{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bgm":"bgm03_story06","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"nameNarration":"Iroha","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"What just happened?!@How could this... What?!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"Um, right... There was a pretty@girl moving one of the mirrors!"},{"narration":"And then the mirror glinted in the light,@and then poof! Yachiyo was gone!"},{"narration":"So she's gone...because..."},{"bg":"bg_adv_91181.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":300,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kaede","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"What...on earth..."},{"bgEffect":"shakeSmall","chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":1,"mouthOpen":1,"tear":1}],"textBg":"shout","textCenter":"...just happened here?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2},{"effect":"fadeout","id":101100}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"H-hey!@You...Ami, was it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Ria","textLeft":"...Yes?"},{"textRight":"Umm... That mirror... Maybe she @vanished because you pointed it at her?"},{"chara":[{"id":301000,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"…"},{"chara":[{"id":301000,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"That seems to be the case!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Trying to put a happy face@on it doesn't make it better..."},{"bgEffect":"shakeSmall","chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":200}],"textBg":"shout","textLeft":"...It was an accident!"},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":300,"pos":2,"tear":0}],"nameRight":"Kaede","textRight":"W-well yeah, but..."},{"nameLeft":"Ria","textLeft":"I didn't do it on purpose!"},{"textLeft":"All I did was just show her@how good I look in this mirror!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"And I think that's what caused@her to disappear..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":200,"tear":0}],"textLeft":"I understand that much!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Okay... @So you do understand what's happening...."},{"textLeft":"But I didn't know that showing her @how good I look would cause all this!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"The Endless Mirrors are unpredictable...@...I had no idea this would happen...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"That's why we call them accidents, right?!"},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":0,"pos":2,"tear":0}],"nameRight":"Kaede","textRight":"I can't believe Yachiyo's gone, too..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":1,"mouthOpen":1,"tear":1}],"textRight":"Hng... *Sniff!*"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Kaede, it's okay..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"I'm innocent!"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1}],"textRight":"Kaede...@She's gonna be okay, I'm sure of it!"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story15","textRight":"And Momoko and Rena are, too!"},{"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":301}],"textRight":"...I'm sorry... @I know that must not be very convincing..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":101100,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"pos":2,"tear":1}],"nameRight":"Kaede","textRight":"…@[chara:101100:lipSynch_1]No, it helps…"},{"textRight":"Thank you, Iroha..."},{"chara":[{"id":301000,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"…"},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301000,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"[chara:300100:lipSynch_0](...I'm not the bad guy here...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Come on...@We have to go look for them!"},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":200,"pos":2,"tear":1}],"nameRight":"Kaede","textRight":"Yeah!"},{"chara":[{"effect":"slideOutRight","face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101100},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301000,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"[chara:300100:lipSynch_0](They're really going to go...)"},{"chara":[{"id":301000,"lipSynch":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Ria","textCenter":"[chara:300100:lipSynch_0](They did it... They really left...)"},{"chara":[{"id":301000,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"[chara:300100:lipSynch_0](They just waved goodbye...)"},{"chara":[{"id":301000,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"[chara:300100:lipSynch_0](...And now they're gone...)"},{"chara":[{"id":301000,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"[chara:300100:lipSynch_0]..."},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301000,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200}],"textBg":"shout","textCenter":"W-wait! @Wait just a minute!"},{"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2},{"effect":"fadeout","id":301000}],"nameRight":"Kaede","textRight":"Whoa![chara:101100:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"What...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"I want to help you.@...Help you find her, I mean..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kaede","textRight":"You...do?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":100100,"motion":401,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"But you don't have to..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"It's no problem, really! Of course @I'm busy, but I can spare some time!"},{"textLeft":"But I feel I should remind you @that I'm not the bad guy here!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kaede","textRight":"What do you think, Iroha...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"Well... The more people in@a search party, the better..."},{"textRight":"Maybe we...should accept her help?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301000,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"Good!@Then it's settled!"},{"chara":[{"id":301000,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"We'll start by looking over here!@Follow me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101100,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kaede","textRight":"[chara:301000:effect_slideOutLeft]Wait, wait, what?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Iroha","textRight":"H-hang on a second!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":2}